(1002, 612, 'short-description', 'a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:17:"short-description";s:143:"Spiders are invertebrates with a two part body (phalo thorax and abdomen), biting chelicerae and silk glands that discharge through spinnerets.";}}'),
