(4, 1, '2015-06-28 14:52:09', '2015-06-28 14:52:09', '<div class="home_content">\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h1>Pest Control Blacktown - Allrid Pest Services</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOffering you our outstanding pest control service and using the safest and most effective pesticides available in the marketplace. At Allrid Pest Services, you can be assured that you’ll be dealing with experienced pest control professionals in the business.\r\n\r\nOur priority is looking after your home, investment or workplace. Servicing the Sydney metropolitan area we can assist with those pesky problems on all residential, commercial and industrial sites.\r\n\r\nWe are dedicated to providing the most effective pest control service, using the highest quality products and equipment every time, all at a competitive &amp; affordable price.\r\n\r\nThe chemicals we use are both child and pet friendly, whilst successful in the elimination of unwanted pests.\r\n\r\nWhen we treat your home or business it will be done to the highest standards.\r\n\r\nOur technicians are all fully accredited, licensed and insured. You can rest assure when you call us you’ll be served with professional, quality, trained and certified staff all working to the strictest health and safety industry standards.\r\n\r\nWe are proud of our workmanship and use environmentally friendly products, safe for your family and pets.\r\n\r\n<strong>Call 0414 467 981 today for an effective pest control service!</strong>\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h2>Our Pest Control Service Areas</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAll suburbs of Sydney, including Castle Hill, Kellyville, Baulkham Hills, West Pennant Hills, Cherrybrook, Dural, Glenhaven, Bella Vista, Winston Hills, Northmead, Rouse Hill, Glenwood, Stanhope Garden, Seven Hills, Blacktown, Quakers Hill, Parramatta, Merrylands, Guildford.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Landing Page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'landing-page', '', '', '2016-05-05 09:05:41', '2016-05-05 09:05:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/?page_id=4', 0, 'page', '', 0),
