(8, 1, '2015-06-29 15:29:07', '2015-06-29 15:29:07', 'With extensive experience in the industry and working with industry leaders, we have taken onboard a range of knowledge and skills that work. To be able to offer to you the finest and professional services available.   \r\n\r\nWe take the time to listen and assist with your pest control problem, as there is a course of action that needs to be followed. The most important stage is the pest identification stage; this determines what the pest issues are and what we are dealing with.  From here, we can establish and advise the best ways to resolve and eradicate the problem.\r\n\r\nWe ensure our clients are happy with both the quality and service of our work and their understanding of what we do and how we do it.\r\n\r\nWe are a small experienced team, which is able to call upon a broad range of skills to offer you preventative strategies for your pest problems.\r\n\r\nAt Allrid Pest Services we have highly trained and qualified technicians that offer professional, effective and quality treatments. \r\n\r\nWith our extensive knowledge and experience with pest control solutions, we provide our clients with truthful, professional advice and offer personalised solutions to solve your pest control problems.\r\n\r\nCall our friendly staff on (02)8809 7945 or 0414 467 981 for a free quote or advice on all your pest control needs.', 'Who we are', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'who-we-are', '', '', '2015-08-02 17:18:49', '2015-08-02 17:18:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
