(10, 1, '2015-06-29 15:29:20', '2015-06-29 15:29:20', '<div class="imagewidth100"><img src="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/pest-free-family1.jpg" alt="Residential Pest control"/></div>\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h1>Residential Pest control</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt Allrid Pest Services we understand the importance of health and safety for your family and home. That’s why when you call Allrid Pest Services you’ll get quality personal service, as your number one priority is also our number one priority!\r\n\r\nWe are here to assist eliminate pests from your home, using the safest health and environmentally friendly products available in the marketplace. Protecting your home and family from cockroaches, spiders, silverfish, birds, rodents, termites and other pests which carry diseases and can be harmful to you and your loved ones.\r\n\r\nWhen we treat your home, we will leave your property just as clean as when we arrived.\r\n\r\nOur clients will always receive reliable, professional on- time service, every time- that’s our guarantee!\r\n\r\nAs an Allrid Pest Services client you’ll always come first.\r\n\r\nWe are here to successfully eliminate unwanted pests in your property. Our company provides you with effective pest management solutions in Sydney.\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h2>Our services include:</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>General Pest Control</li>\r\n	<li>Termite Control</li>\r\n	<li>Cockroach Control</li>\r\n	<li>Mouse and Rat (Rodents) Control</li>\r\n	<li>Ant Control</li>\r\n	<li>Wasp and Bees Control</li>\r\n	<li>Fleas Control</li>\r\n	<li>Spider Control</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAllrid Pest Services understands the impact and reflection pests can have on your home.\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h2>For reliable and honest pest control call - Allrid Pest Services</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>On time service</strong>\r\nWe are on-call providing you with reliable on time service. With our extensive knowledge and experience with pest control solutions, we provide our clients with truthful, professional advice and offer personalised solutions to solve your pest control problems.\r\n\r\n<strong>Affordable prices</strong>\r\nProviding you the finest and professional services available all at competitive pricing.', 'Your Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'residential-pest-control', '', '', '2016-06-02 13:33:20', '2016-06-02 13:33:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
