(34, 1, '2015-06-29 15:33:00', '2015-06-29 15:33:00', '<div class="google_map_container">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h1>Allrid Pest Services</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>We are a small experienced team, which is able to call upon a broad range of skills to offer you preventative pest control strategies for your pest problems.</div>\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h3>Our Pest Control Services</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/residential-pest-control/">General Pest Control</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/termite-inspection-treatment-protection/">Termite Inspection, Treatment &amp; Protection</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-list/cockroaches/">Cockroach Control</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-control/rodents-rat-mice/">Mouse and Rat (Rodents) Control</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-list/ants/">Ant Control</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-list/bees/">Wasp and Bees Removal</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-list/fleas/">Fleas Control</a>\r\n• <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-list/spiders/">Spider Control</a>\r\n<div class="page_header">\r\n<h3>Our Pest Control Service Areas</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThough we are based in Blacktown, we service all suburbs of Sydney, including <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-control-castle-hilll/">Castle Hill</a>, <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-control-kellyville/">Kellyville</a>, <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-control-baulkham-hills/">Baulkham Hills</a>, West Pennant Hills, Cherrybrook, Dural, Glenhaven, Bella Vista, Winston Hills, Northmead, Rouse Hill, Glenwood, Stanhope Garden, <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-control-seven-hills-area/">Seven Hills</a>, Quakers Hill, <a href="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/pest-control-parramatta/">Parramatta</a