(70, 1, '2015-06-29 16:06:34', '2015-06-29 16:06:34', '<div class="home_content">\r\n		 					<h4>The Pests We Treat</h4>\r\n		 					<p>\r\n		 						Rebel Pest Professionals qualified pest control technicians are ready to remove all those unwanted pests living in your home. The worst by far are Termites – they are the most damaging and costly pests to attack property. Next in line are Cockroaches, Spiders and Rodents – these pests carry diseases that are easily spread through your home affecting the health and safety of your family and pets. But the list doesn’t stop here – we also treat bees, fleas, ants, bed bugs, bird lice, crickets, scorpions, silverfish. We are also registered and licensed to carry out possum catching and release.\r\n		 					</p>\r\n		 				</div>\r\n\r\n		 				<div class="home_content">\r\n		 					<h4>Areas We Service</h4>\r\n		 					<p>\r\n		 						All suburbs of Newcastle, Lake Macquarie, Port Stephens, Maitland, Wine Country (Cessnock/Kurri), Singleton, Denman, Muswellbrook, Scone, Merriwa & Murrurundi and surrounding areas.\r\n		 					</p>\r\n		 				</div>\r\n\r\n		 				<div class="home_content">\r\n		 					<h4>Our Commitment to You</h4>\r\n		 					<p>\r\n		 						At Rebel Pest Professionals, we promise you that all of our pest control technicians are fully qualified, trained to the highest standard, and will carry out the most comprehensive service you have ever received before.\r\n		 					</p>\r\n		 					<p>We also promise to communicate clearly and effectively to give you the peace of mind you deserve.</p>\r\n		 					<p>Our office staff  also have extensive training in all areas of Pest Control and can answer any questions or concerns you may have. Customer service in all aspects is a priority at Rebel Pest Professionals.</p>\r\n		 				</div>', 'Landing Page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-29 16:06:34', '2015-06-29 16:06:34', '', 4, 'http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision',