mber, living in decayed wood that they may excavate to house their nest.  Their workings are clean and free from the faecal marks that are often characteristics of termite workings.\r\n\r\nTermites live in colonies, which are assemblages of different individuals with definite functions or tasks.  The size of the colony varies from a few hundred, as in Neotermes insularis, to hundreds of thousands or even millions, as in the mound-buildings species Nasutitermes and Coptotermes, and also the destructive Mastotermes darwiniensis.\r\n\r\nThe colony takes various forms, some species build mounds, some nest underground and some live in small colonies in trees.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="second_container"><img class="" title="Nasutitermes Termites" src="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/wp-content/themes/allrid/images/termites-treatment-control.jpg" alt="Termites treatment &amp; control" /> Nasutitermes Termites</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imgagewidth33">\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="263"]<img class="" title="Coptotermes Termites" src="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/wp-content/themes/allrid/images/coptotermes_termites.jpg" alt="Coptotermes termites control" width="263" height="152" /> Coptotermes Termites[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imgagewidth33">\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="263"]<img class="" title="Heterotermes Termites" src="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/wp-content/themes/allrid/images/Heterotermes_termites.jpg" alt="Heterotermes termites control" width="267" height="152" /> Heterotermes Termites[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imgagewidth33">\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="263"]<img class="" title="Schedorhinotermes Termites" src="http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/wp-content/themes/allrid/images/Schedorhinotermes_termites.jpg" alt="Schedorhinotermes termites control" width="263" height="152" /> Schedorhinotermes Termites[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Termites', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '619-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-31 08:35:36', '2015-08-31 08:35:36', '', 619, 'http://localhost/allridspestcontrol/619-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
